Levy Restaurants / Compass Group – Spectrum Center & Bank of America Stadium
IT Support Specialist | Charlotte, NC
2021 – Present (Event-Based / Part-Time)
	•	Provide on-site technical support during major NBA, NFL, MLS, and event operations at Spectrum Center and Bank of America Stadium.
	•	Troubleshoot, configure, and maintain 150+ POS terminals, kiosks, handheld devices, printers, and peripherals across multiple concession zones.
	•	Perform real-time diagnostics of network connectivity issues (Ethernet, USB, routers, switches, cabling) to ensure uninterrupted transaction flow during high-volume events.
	•	Monitor POS performance throughout events; proactively complete system checks, hard reboots, and workstation resets following open/close procedures.
	•	Collaborate directly with Levy management, concession leads, and operations teams to resolve IT issues under urgent, time-sensitive conditions.
	•	Assist with onboarding, setup, and technical orientation for new operators and vendors for concerts, sporting events, and special events.
	•	Document recurring issues and escalate hardware, software, and infrastructure concerns to Compass Group IT leadership for long-term resolution.
	•	Ensure compliance with Levy/Compass IT policies, security procedures, and operational standards.
